sellerCard.description: I am working as a front end web developer with more than two years of experience. Also, specialized in front end technologies. I have a strong grip on Bootstrap, Javascript, Html, Jquery, PSD to HTML convert, and css3. If you are looking for an awesome and attractive front end website at an affordable price, then do not hesitate to contact me.

description.content:
Do you need expert html, css & bootstrap developer?? Who can develop or redevelop your professional static html website, so great you're at the right and perfect place!

I will design and develop static responsive portfolio, business, startups companies, real estate, hotels, and travel agency groups website. If you have a psd I will convert it for you into a static one page site.It will be a completely responsive site.


I can help you in following

  • Psd to html
  • Fast Loading Static website development.
  • Using Html, Css & Bootstrap.
  • Mobile Responsive design.
  • Responsive portfolio with html, css, js, jQuery , bootstrap.
  • Animations, Sliders, Contact Form and More
  • Template customization.
  • Site speed optimization


what will you get free?


  • Server upload.
  • Content upload.
  • Seo friendly.
  • Free github hosting.

 

What do I need from you?

  • I need an overview of your business.
  • Your brand name/organization logo (if you don't have any no worries I'll design Basic One)
  • Your favorite site as an example. (Optional)
  • The images and the design if you have any.
  • Color scheme (Option
